des:
Following the Roaming Stones Family on their adventure? 

Just say, "Alexa, ask the Roaming Stones Family for an update!"

This skill is designed to keep you up-to-date on the family and their itinerary as they roam around the world for the rest of 2018. It also features information about the countries they're in and other fun facts. Check back each week for something new!
